WILLOVER (Norman) on H.C. No. S226523. Supreme Court of California Aug. 10, 2016. CANTIL-SAKAUYE, C.J., WERDEGAR, CHIN, CORRIGAN, LIU, CUÉLLAR, and KRUGER, JJ., concur.

Dismissed and remanded to CA 6.

In light of the decision in Montgomery v. Louisiana (2016) ---U.S. ----, 136 S.Ct. 718 , 193 L.Ed.2d 599 , review in the above-entitled matter is dismissed. (Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.528(b)(1).)
